\par\pard\plain \tx0\li346\fi14\sb60\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf8 - Sarah:}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::2> Sarah is in a state of euphoria. She's feeling think she's never felt before. She is in a condition that might be called trucking bliss. A timeless state, where very little of the outside world matters in the moment.<!$Scr_Cs::2>}
\par\plain {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf8 - Evan:}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::2> Evan could not be happier with the way the evening went. He did have unspoken concerns at the beginning of the day, that Sarah would shut down around her family like she does around his friends. But quite the opposite happened. Not only was Sarah engaged in the nights conversation activities, she often played center stage in a Christmas Eve smashing success. Evan always feels love for Sarah, but the dominating feeling at the moment was, pride.<!$Scr_Cs::2><!$Scr_Ps::5>}
