\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\fi360\sa120\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 <$Scr_Ps::4>Sarah and Evan find themselves back in the room, getting ready for bed. Evan told Sarah he was going to brush his teeth and offered to let her use the bathroom first. Sarah is in a state that might be called "drunken euphoria" or "blissful euphoria." It's a surreal feeling beyond anything she'd ever experienced before. Evan took her lack of an answer as the okay to go ahead and use the restroom first.}
